- Apple Watch Shock Proof Tempered Glass Case

- Specifically designed for Apple Watch to provide all-around protection.

- Constructed with durable materials, including tempered glass and shockproof features.

- Offers full coverage to safeguard the watch from impacts, scratches, and daily wear.

- Easy to install and remove, ensuring hassle-free usage.

- Maintains the touch sensitivity and functionality of the watch.

- The tempered glass adds an extra layer of protection to the watch face.

- Shockproof design absorbs and disperses impact to minimize damage.

- Available in various sizes and styles to match different Apple Watch models.

- A practical choice for those who want to protect their Apple Watch without compromising its style and functionality.

- The Apple Watch Shock Proof Tempered Glass Case is a reliable solution for keeping your Apple Watch safe from potential damage caused by impacts and daily wear. Its combination of tempered glass and shockproof features offers comprehensive protection for your watch while maintaining its sleek appearance. Whether you're engaging in active activities or simply want to keep your watch safe from accidental bumps, this case provides the necessary defense to preserve the integrity of your Apple Watch.

column2: USB Charger Cable For Fitbit Charge 6 5 4 3 2 Ace Inspire Versa Luxe Ionic Sense (Fitbit Versa 3)
column9:
Compatible Models:
Replacement charging cables are specially designed for Charge 5 and Luxe only. It will keeps your fitness tracker always alive.

Upgraded Strong Magnet:
According to customer voice and market research, we continuously optimize the magnetic attraction strength, and the upgraded version can provide a strong and stable connection after testing.

Safe & Fast:
Passed thousands of qualified tests, it can provide a fast as original charging speed and stable charging environment to ensure that your watch is safer to charge.

Durable & Stable:
Made of high quality ABS plastic and TPE cable, lightweight, environmentally friendly, stable and durable, giving you a good charging experience.

Simply & Portable:
Charging cord provides you convenient use and the flexibility you need. Also Can charge with screen protector and bands on.

Easy to Use:
Just simply plug your Luxe or Charge 5 into USB port on your PC, laptop, power bank, wall charger or car charger to charge.

Specifications:
Type: USB Charging Cable
Sport/Activity: Gym & Training, Running & Jogging
Colour: Black
Cable Length: 1M
Material: Rubber

Package Included:
1X USB Charging Cable for Fitbit
